00:00:31.850 --> 00:00:34.780 align:middle line:84%
So very little has been known
about the unique capabilities

00:00:34.780 --> 00:00:37.840 align:middle line:84%
of the female mind,
which you've made it

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:39.800 align:middle line:84%
your life's work,
your passion, in fact.

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:41.800 align:middle line:84%
You gave us a lot of food
for thought last time.

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:45.560 align:middle line:84%
And since then, you have
since gained your PhD in--

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:48.042 align:middle line:84%
let me say it right--
neuro-psychophysiology.

00:00:48.042 --> 00:00:49.000 align:middle line:90%
>>KAYLA OSTERHOFF: Yes.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:50.752 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So, congratulations.

00:00:50.752 --> 00:00:51.710 align:middle line:90%
>>OSTERHOFF: Thank you.

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:54.620 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: There's so much being
discovered almost by the day.

00:00:54.620 --> 00:00:57.730 align:middle line:84%
